{"data":[{"id":561654949,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"481b524ca3f6ebd23a7f3608c66758fb","url_token":"chang-cheng-4-70","name":"不动声色","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-bb22c5d2bcc6d2bafc76ffc7f3fa2e16_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-bb22c5d2bcc6d2bafc76ffc7f3fa2e16_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/481b524ca3f6ebd23a7f3608c66758fb","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":26,"is_followed":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561654949","thumbnail":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-76d9426ae7806b0586b9d8fff8830de2_200x112.jpg","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545986605,"updated_time":1546278705,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":28,"comment_count":2,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"all","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"\u003cp\u003e好了，不懂、不尊重又不敬畏数学的人，你们的梦醒了么？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e看完证明，我觉得我就是那个头像上的猴子 ，我们每个人都是猴子。争辩来争辩去，有意思吗？真xx浪费时间！\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e真可笑！\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e---------\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这是我最新的更新。昨晚睡不着打开看各路答主的回答，在评论里发现了很神奇的事，当然真假我也很难说，发出来让大家都看看。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-cb6a8477f23b32b9c92e2940566b9fce_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"1440\" data-rawheight=\"1634\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-726a5c0aceabd37339f3433154fbbc0e_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1440\" data-original=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-cb6a8477f23b32b9c92e2940566b9fce_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1440'%20height='1634'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"1440\" data-rawheight=\"1634\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-726a5c0aceabd37339f3433154fbbc0e_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1440\" data-original=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-cb6a8477f23b32b9c92e2940566b9fce_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-cb6a8477f23b32b9c92e2940566b9fce_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-551258780195c964b636b6cb0bb41b93_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"1440\" data-rawheight=\"1932\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-a3a01a68830060b62a5de63d8728b90f_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1440\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-551258780195c964b636b6cb0bb41b93_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1440'%20height='1932'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"1440\" data-rawheight=\"1932\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-a3a01a68830060b62a5de63d8728b90f_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1440\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-551258780195c964b636b6cb0bb41b93_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-551258780195c964b636b6cb0bb41b93_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-0d5746be74ad8f2d38df5cc23fbc24fe_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"1440\" data-rawheight=\"947\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-1c925657f6c7a976030b04884d9380c1_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1440\" data-original=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-0d5746be74ad8f2d38df5cc23fbc24fe_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1440'%20height='947'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"1440\" data-rawheight=\"947\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-1c925657f6c7a976030b04884d9380c1_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1440\" data-original=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-0d5746be74ad8f2d38df5cc23fbc24fe_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-0d5746be74ad8f2d38df5cc23fbc24fe_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e---------\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我看到这个问题是很愤怒的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e因为我喜欢数学。我觉得数学是那么的神奇而有魅力，那一条一条的定理如同一个一个的台阶，是无数大师一步一步迈进而得到的伟大成果。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e不是说高中生就不行，我只是讨厌民科一般的论调，博人眼球的做法真的很让人厌恶。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e不尊重科学的人，我相信永远不会被科学青睐。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我看到这个问题下的回答更愤怒，还有好多人在评论里对数学工作者嘲讽，甚至各种打压天才的阴谋论......\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e唉，我真的不知道说什么好，很失望，真的很失望。相信热爱数学的人看到这样的评论也是跟我一样的心情吧，想说什么又说不出来。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e想了一肚子的脏话，最后只憋出来一句:哗众取宠的跳梁小丑！\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e-------\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e刚才看到许多圣母说要知乎er演算他的证明，说数学工作者动不动上纲上线。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e遇到这种人我只想说:每年有那么多民科说自己研究出了这个定理那个定理的，难道数学工作者还要一个一个为他们演算一遍?就算演算出来，人家不懂也没办法，到时还会跳出一些人来说:看，天才的思维总是不被世人接受，而且还要被所谓的一个个大师所打压。这样的例子在以前也有很多了。试想一下，别人对你热爱的东西不放在眼里，丝毫没有一点点的敬畏之心和尊重，而且底下还有很多不明所以的人支持他，你的心里能好受?\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e---------\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e贴一个我和一位答主的争论，没有要嘲讽这个答主的意思，只是表明我的态度和看法。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-261f824fbaae711a7c77686c46266d76_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"1440\" data-rawheight=\"1525\" data-size=\"normal\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1440\" data-original=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-261f824fbaae711a7c77686c46266d76_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1440'%20height='1525'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"1440\" data-rawheight=\"1525\" data-size=\"normal\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1440\" data-original=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-261f824fbaae711a7c77686c46266d76_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-261f824fbaae711a7c77686c46266d76_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-0e1d791a6d7f9e192976ac217b60a323_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"1440\" data-rawheight=\"1756\" data-size=\"normal\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1440\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-0e1d791a6d7f9e192976ac217b60a323_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1440'%20height='1756'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"1440\" data-rawheight=\"1756\" data-size=\"normal\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1440\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-0e1d791a6d7f9e192976ac217b60a323_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-0e1d791a6d7f9e192976ac217b60a323_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-95a61ac56be46eb6be8cceeee785afa5_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"1440\" data-rawheight=\"1916\" data-size=\"normal\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1440\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-95a61ac56be46eb6be8cceeee785afa5_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1440'%20height='1916'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"1440\" data-rawheight=\"1916\" data-size=\"normal\